Carrie Mathison (Tara Lynn Foxx), a bipolar CIA officer, is told by an informant that an American prisoner of war has been turned. Convinced that 'turned' means 'gay', she sets her sights on U.S. Marine sergeant Nicholas Brody (Richie Calhoun), and becomes obsessed with uncovering the truth behind the alleged war hero. Featuring a stellar cast, a hysterical script, and standout acting performances by Foxx and Calhoun, 'This Ain't Homeland XXX' is the hottest, funniest porn parody of the year!
